    {
      "name": "collect_protocol_fees",
      "docs": [
        "Collect protocol fees from a Cubic Pool",
        "",
        "### Authority",
        "- \"collect_protocol_fees_authority\" - Authority from config",
        "",
        "### remaining_accounts",
        "For each token in the pool (in order):",
        "- vault: TokenAccount - Pool's token vault (writable)",
        "- recipient: TokenAccount - Authority's recipient account (writable)"
      ],
