        "",
        "### Parameters",
        "- `amount_in` - The amount of input token to swap",
        "- `minimum_amount_out` - The minimum amount of output token expected",
        "- `token_in_index` - Index of the input token in the pool",
        "- `token_out_index` - Index of the output token in the pool",
        "",
        "#### Special Errors",
        "- `InvalidTokenIndex` - Token index out of bounds",
        "- `InsufficientLiquidity` - Not enough liquidity in the pool",
        "- `SlippageExceeded` - Output amount less than minimum"
      ],
